Package: toxODmeta
Title: Find Optimal Designs in Toxicology using Metaheuristics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Will", "Gertsch", , "willgertsch@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tool for finding optimal designs for common toxicology models using metaheuristics from the metaheuristicOpt package. An R Shiny app is included to make finding designs easy even without coding knowledge.
